data.description: This exclusive, luxurious home is absolutely stunning and located in a desired neighborhood in Virginia Beach. Featuring 6 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, a first-floor bedroom, an office, a massive primary bedroom, an enormous bonus room, queen sized bedrooms & a backyard oasis. Enjoy entertaining in your gorgeous kitchen, boasting the most beautiful quartz island, backsplash, granite countertops and grand, open-concept living. You will love the detailed feature walls, the exquisite lighting, crown molding, plantation shutters, an oversized mudroom, three-car garage, permanent, customizable outdoor home LED lighting, sound system & so much more! Relax in the in the hot tub, visit by the stunning, stone fire-pit, read a book on your TREX deck or float in your large saltwater pool. Miles to Sandbridge Beach and military installations!
